dialogSubtitle:
Hi I have good news and bad news :(
The bad news is that SensiX Xarena will not be updated anymore, because there are too many bugs and errors, and the good news is that I created a new SensiV Xarena application that has been released on the Telegram :)

Hai, Saya punya Kabar baik dan kabar buruk :(
Kabar buruknya SensiX Xarena idak akan di perbarui lagi, karena terlalu banyak bug dan error, dan kabar baiknya saya membuat aplikasi baru SensiV Xarena yang sudah rilis di Telegram :)
dialogInfo: [INFO] "SensiV Xarena" Has been released, you can try app on Telegram
